data.description: Are you interested in an adorable 2-bedroom, 1-bath home located near the Medford Railroad Park, shopping and dining? This home is perfect for first-time buyers or investors looking for a cozy space of just over 1000 square feet. The AC unit was replaced in 2021, and the purchase includes the gazebo and larger shed in the backyard as well! The seller is motivated, so this could be a great opportunity for you!
